  <description><![CDATA[<p>Offering comfortable accommodation in <a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel">Courchevel</a>, this hotel is an excellent choice if you are looking to be close to the vibrant resort centre and the extensive Three Valleys ski slopes.</p>
<h2>Comfortable Accommodation</h2>
<p>This hotel has been renovated over the recent seasons providing more comfort to guests, and with just 36 bedrooms the hotel has a great friendly and cosy atmosphere. The rooms are furnished in a modern Alpine style with many of the rooms having a balcony so you can look out onto the resort or across the valley.</p>
<p>Relax at the end of your day on the slopes in the comfortable lounge area on the third floor and admire the wonderful views over the valley. The hotel breakfast room has spectacular mountain views, and these views can also be enjoyed from most of the bedrooms balconies.</p>
<h2>Central Location</h2>
<p>The Hotel Les Cascades is situated in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel">Courchevel</a> Moriond (1650), with the local shops, cafes and bars being just a short walk away. The hotel benefits from being directly opposite the ski lifts and pistes giving you easy access onto the renowned <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area</a>. Explore the 600km of pistes or make the most of the sunny slopes surrounding Moriond. </p>
<p>Courchevel is known for its lively and vibrant après scene, and there are plenty of bars surrounding the hotel. If you are after somewhere to go for dinner, you can find a number of restaurants serving regional cuisine, pizza, pasta and burgers dotted around the resort.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
